{
  "stem": "13251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although, in Ely, we had gentiles going there also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it wasn't just for refugees from Europe, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Jewish Free School was for Jewish people, so for Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--what?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, hearing, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to have air raids [LAUGHS] frequently in Ely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we used to hear, you know, the-- the sirens going at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'd have to go get out of bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we go downstairs, into-- to the-- into the ground floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would sit underneath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Usually, there was like a staircase, which I guess they thought that was the safest place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we'd sit there for the duration of the air raid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--how my stomach used to go, when we used to hear planes overhead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was silent, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you'd hear a plane coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you'd wonder, is it a-- is it ours or-- or somebody else's, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Not that much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The thing is that Ely, even though we were north, we had a-- an air field not far from Ely.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go visit it sometimes-- walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a few miles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to go visit over there and pick blackberries as kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had these four-- four-engine bombers that used to-- used to, you know, go on missions almost every night to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I think one of the biggest airfields was right near Ely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I don't know if that was significant or what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I wouldn't say it was a lot, those air raids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was enough to-- to-- to get you-- kinda-- I remember my stomach used to go like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then of course, you'd hear these bombs go off.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
